Package: fmesher
Type: Package
Title: Triangle Meshes and Other Geometry Tools
Version: 0.0.7.9001
Author: Finn Lindgren <finn.lindgren@gmail.com>
Maintainer: Finn Lindgren <finn.lindgren@gmail.com>
Description: Functions that generate planar and spherical triangle meshes for
    finite element calculations, and functions for lines and polygons. Experimental
    package that will take over these features from the INLA package.
Depends:
    Matrix
Suggests:
    INLA,
    testthat (>= 3.0.0),
    covr
Imports:
    graphics,
    grDevices,
    fields,
    methods,
    rgeos,
    rgdal,
    R.methodsS3,
    sp,
    stats,
    utils,
    withr
Additional_repositories: https://inla.r-inla-download.org/R/testing
URL: https://inlabru-org.github.io/fmesher/
BugReports: https://github.com/inlabru-org/fmesher/issues
License: GPL (>=3)
Copyright: The R package and code, and the main programs, were written by and
    are Copyright by Finn Lindgren, and are redistributable under the GNU Public
    License, version 3 or later.
NeedsCompilation: no
RoxygenNote: 7.1.1
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
Config/testthat/edition: 3
Config/testthat/parallel: true
